text: This transmits obsolete IRM 1.35.9, Financial Accounting, Integrated Financial System Payroll.

This IRM is obsolete as the IRM content is contained in standard operating procedures (SOP) on the following site (S:\IFM\OFMS\Office of Financial Management Systems\Ancillary Systems\Ancillary Systems Procedures\Payroll AINFC). The content consists of information for the CFO Ancillary Systems team on how to process payroll data into Integrated Financial System (IFS).
